Test Plan

Objective
The objective is to test the functionality of the MakersBnB. Looking at what is in the scope and prioritizing them in line with the how much it would affect the user. 

Scope
Sign up
Log in / log out
Create spaces
Edit spaces
Set availability
Request bookings
Approve / deny requests

Lower Priority
Payments
Chat
Email/SMS notifications

Priority Areas
P0: Booking flow, double booking prevention, request approval
P1: Space creation, editing, availability
P2: Authentication
P3: Notifications, chat, payments


Exploratory Testing Session Plan (90 minutes)

0–15 mins: Authentication
Sign up with valid and invalid data
Test password validation
Log in and log out
Attempt access without authentication


15–35 mins: Space Management
Create a space with valid data
Try missing required fields
Enter long or unusual inputs
Create multiple spaces

35–60 mins: Booking Flow
Browse spaces
Request a booking e.g past dates, overlapping dates, unavailable dates
Observe booking status changes

60–75 mins: Request Handling
Approve a request
Deny a request
Verify status updates
Check availability updates after approval

75–90 mins: Edge Cases & Multi-user

Attempt double booking with 2 users
Submit simultaneous requests
Refresh during booking flow
Use browser navigation (back/forward)
